<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٩٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تعطي صدقة الفطر عمن <span class="c2">(تمون)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> من أهلها: <span class="c2">(الشاهد)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> و <span class="c2">(الغائب)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
